rror_file_</i>47̷͈̎ζ̷̗̾≢̢̳̔͆ ̸̽ͅξ̶͇̝͗</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369010/extras/2816b60109e8fbdd7e955a39941e93f8.poster.avif?t=1766028556\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369010/extras/2816b60109e8fbdd7e955a39941e93f8.webm?t=1766028556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3369010/extras/2816b60109e8fbdd7e955a39941e93f8.mp4?t=1766028556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We'll still leave the game on Steam in case someone wants to solve this weird mystery. Just don't get your hopes up. Oh and by the way, the game doesn't even close. Some of our computers seem a bit messed up since we installed it. Legal notice: Our company won't be held liable for any damage it caused.</p>",
